{"tid":2408122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[初三赤口]炮台山harbour grand你執柒左佢啦","createTime":"2021-02-14T15:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T11:54:50.000Z","uid":110020,"like":47,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3311e9a459f38b76ed3b4822d8683283e3749615","tid":2408122,"uid":110020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">依加香港時間11:41pm</span></span><br />\n今日情人節好地地book左炮台山harbour grand個 staycation套餐<br />\n有1400餐飲credit要係酒店內食左佢<br />\n情人節都預左多人 checkin check好耐唔講啦 <br />\n夜晚個餐無左晚市要room service 我地都諗住要等下嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">好啦7點12分落左個單</span> 佢同我講要等兩個鐘<br />\nokay可以接受 我就戇鳩鳩開心的等<br />\n到左9點 好仲未有 再俾啲耐性佢等多陣<br />\n好差唔多10點 個肚打撚曬鼓 打去前台問話有未<br />\n條線feel到已經爆左 播左十分鐘音樂先有人聽<br />\n話幫緊你幫緊你check張單轉頭打翻俾你<br />\n<br />\n之後佢覆我 errrr今日真係好多客唔好意思 <span class=\"x-large\">你張單應該要11點零先到</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">屌你11點零先到你煮乜撚野煮四個鐘啊 隻豬劏緊定捉緊啊<br />\n定法國餐要分4個鐘一餐啊<br />\n啲廚走曬無人煮你執柒左佢啦你學乜人開酒店啊誠哥</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後10點半落街買野食 初三乜都無開<br />\n迫住買7仔充飢 果然初三真係赤口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTzxiBc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTzxiBc.png&h=3237a3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加我舊豬扒都仲未到<br />\n聽講樓下lobby有人報左警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cab4a6689bd5638bad4ad62dab6d354c7b329fc","tid":2408122,"uid":164523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<br />\n咁依加有得食未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c7e9517b027f801a57dd3c9d1eb1fc2c2582c2","tid":2408122,"uid":110020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5cab4a6689bd5638bad4ad62dab6d354c7b329fc","tid":2408122,"uid":164523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<br />\n咁依加有得食未？<img src=